---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import Testimonials from '../components/Testimonials.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
const title = "Mobile Tyres, Puncture Repairs, TPMS, Batteries"
const description = "Freeway Mobile Tyres are one of Dorset's leading mobile tyre services. We'll come to you at home, work or roadside and fit your tyres today."
const bgImg = "url(/img/services/freeway-mobile-tyres.webp)"
const heading = "Why Spend Hours At A Garage?"
const tagline = "We Can Fit Your Tyres At Home, Work or Roadside"
const quoteForm = "size"
---

<Layout title={`${title} | Freeway Mobile Tyres`} description={description}>
    <Hero heading={heading} tagline={tagline} bgImg={bgImg} quoteForm={quoteForm}/>
    <main class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-3 mb-lg-5">Your Local Mobile Tyre Service In Dorset</h1>
            <div class="row text-center text-lg-start">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <p><em>Are you stranded at the side of the road with a flat tyre? Do you need to change your old car tyres but don’t want to spend hours at a garage?</em> Well, you’ve come to the right place!</p>
                    <p>Freeway Mobile Tyres is your local mobile tyre fitting service in Dorset. We come to your location at a time that suits you and replace your tyres today.</p>
                    <p>We can fit tyres to most types of vehicles, including cars, vans, caravans, motorhomes, and trailers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <p>In addition, we are one of the few tyre services in Dorset that provide <strong>same day fitting</strong> and <strong>seven day service</strong>.</p>
                    <p>What’s more, with an average arrival time of less than 60 minutes, we provide one of the fastest mobile tyre replacement services in the area.</p>
                    <p>So what are you waiting for? Contact us today and experience the easy way to change your tyres!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="col-10 offset-1">
    
                <div class="text-center pt-5">
                    <h2 class="mb-3">Our Services</h2>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="Mobile Tyre Fitting" cardText="Tyres Fitted at Home, Work Or Roadside" cardLink="/mobile-tyres/mobile-tyre-fitting">
                                <i class="bi bi-car-front fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="Puncture Repair" cardText="We'll Come To You And Fix Your Flat Tyre" cardLink="/mobile-tyres/puncture-repair">
                                <i class="bi bi-vinyl fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="Caravan Tyre Fitting" cardText="Change Your Caravan Tyres The Easy Way" cardLink="/mobile-tyres/mobile-caravan-tyre-fitting">
                                <i class="bi bi-truck fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="Locking Wheel Nut Removal" cardText="All Car Makes & Models Covered" cardLink="/services/locking-wheel-nut-removal">
                                <i class="bi bi-wrench-adjustable fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="Tyre Pressure Sensors" cardText="TPMS Diagnostics & Repair" cardLink="/services/tyre-pressure-monitoring-system">
                                <i class="bi bi-wifi fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                            <Card cardTitle="AlloyGator Wheel Protectors" cardText="Protect & Style Your Rims" cardLink="/services/alloygator-wheel-protection">
                                <i class="bi bi-shield fs-1 mb-3"></i>
                            </Card>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <Testimonials />
    <CTA />
</Layout>
